---
title: Cal Smart Middle Eastern-Inspired Beef Patties with Mint Tabbouleh and Lemon Aioli
description: Fresh and herbaceous, tabbouleh is a staple in Lebanese fare. It is typically made with parsley, but we've adapted this version with fragrant fresh mint and paired it with spiced beef patties and flavourful lemon aioli.
